---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Pinochle Pro — Classic Pinochle Card Game for iPhone & iPad"
  description="Play classic Pinochle with Bob, Shirley, and Jed. Advanced AI opponents, deep rule customization, and online play coming soon. Free on iOS."
  canonical="/"
>
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Pinochle Pro</h1>
    <p class="tagline">The classic card game — played with Bob, Shirley, and Jed.</p>
    <a href="/pricing" class="play-btn" onclick="gtag && gtag('event', 'play_cta_click', {source: 'hero'})">Play Free →</a>
    <div class="app-badges">
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pinochle-pro/id567644839" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download Pinochle Pro on the App Store" />
      </a>
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pinochle-pro-3-player/id916432421" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download Pinochle Pro 3-Hand on the App Store" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="video-container">
    <video autoplay loop muted preload="none" aria-label="Pinochle Pro gameplay preview">
      <source src="/gameplay-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
  </div>

  <div class="features-section">
    <h2>Why Choose Pinochle Pro?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Bob, Shirley & Jed:</strong> Play against characters inspired by real people — their table talk and reactions make every hand memorable.</li>
      <li><strong>Advanced AI:</strong> Opponents that bid, pass, and play like experienced Pinochle players — not random card throwers.</li>
      <li><strong>Deep Customization:</strong> Starting bid, game end score, card passing, double marriage value, bidding aggressiveness — configure it your way.</li>
      <li><strong>Both Variants:</strong> 4-Hand partnership Pinochle and 3-Hand solo Pinochle with kitty bidding.</li>
      <li><strong>Stats & History:</strong> Track your performance and study your game over time.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="email-capture">
    <h2>Online play is coming.</h2>
    <p>Be the first to know when PinochlePro launches online multiplayer and web play.</p>
    <form
      class="email-form"
      action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/pinochlepro"
      method="post"
      target="_blank"
      onsubmit="window.gtag && gtag('event', 'email_signup', {event_category: 'engagement'});"
    >
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required aria-label="Email address" />
      <button type="submit">Notify Me</button>
    </form>
    <p class="email-fine-print">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2>Free to play. Subscriber features coming soon.</h2>
    <p>The full game is free — all rules, all variants, all AI opponents. Subscribers unlock ad-free play, card themes, AI personalities, and more.</p>
    <a href="/pricing" class="pricing-cta" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:8px;">See Pricing →</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
